          <header class="wu-card-header">
           <h3 class="wu-card-title">
            <a class="link-heading" href="https://diversity.wustl.edu/get-involved/annual-events/">
             Diwali Celebrations
            </a>
           </h3>
          </header>
          <div class="wu-card-content">
           <p class="wu-card-excerpt">
            Diwali, the Hindu “Festival of Lights” has been celebrated at WashU for more than 25 years. Ashoka, the South Asian Student Association, each year presents a major show that celebrates a fusion of South Asian cultures.
           </p>
          </div>
         </article>
         <article class="wu-card bg-turquoise match-height grid-1-3">
